OL,3,CThe women who were pivotal in allowing
OL,4,Cthe miners to strike
OL,6,FDonations came in not just from across
OL,7,Fthe UK, but from supporters around the
OL,8,Fworld.
OL,10,FWhen sought powers to seize the funds,
OL,11,FChristine withdrew the donations from
OL,12,Fthe bank and then hid the cash under
OL,13,Fher bed.
OL,15,FShe says "the support groups were
OL,16,Fvital, a lifeline for striking
OL,17,Ffamilies, fulfilling the role of an
OL,18,Falternative Welfare State."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/14
