OL,3,CThe women who were pivotal in allowing
OL,4,Cthe miners to strike
OL,6,FDavid Williams was a miner in the
OL,7,FBlaenant Colliery in Crynant. Looking
OL,8,Fthrough the box of badges brings back
OL,9,Fmemories.
OL,11,FHe said: "I think it is an
OL,12,Funderstatement. I mean, the strike
OL,13,Fwouldn't have lasted two months
OL,14,Fwithout the support groups because the
OL,15,Fpeople would had been starved out.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/14
