OL,3,CThe women who were pivotal in allowing
OL,4,Cthe miners to strike
OL,6,F"The women's efforts were brilliant.
OL,7,FWithout them, we would have been sunk
OL,8,Flong before we were, long before we
OL,9,Fwere. They can organise, the women can
OL,10,Forganise. There's no two ways about
OL,11,Fit."
OL,13,FOne of those women who organised the
OL,14,Fsupport was Ann Jones who worked in a
OL,15,Flocal sewing factory.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/14
