OL,3,CThe women who were pivotal in allowing
OL,4,Cthe miners to strike
OL,6,F"I think it brought in a lot for women
OL,7,Fwho hadn't done anything before. They
OL,8,Fdidn't think they could do anything. I
OL,9,Fdidn't think I could do anything, I
OL,10,Fthink it gave women pride in
OL,11,Fthemselves. I think it brought more
OL,12,Frespect to women and made a huge
OL,13,Fdifference." Ann explained.
OL,15,FAnn added: "There is still more to do
OL,16,Fto make sure working class women, all
OL,17,Fwomen, have more and equal
OL,18,Fopportunities. It's clear she is still
OL,19,Fa fierce campaigner and an activist at
OL,20,Fheart."
