OL,3,CThe women who were pivotal in allowing
OL,4,Cthe miners to strike
OL,6,FFour decades on and Onllwyn's pit and
OL,7,Fthe coal fields across Wales are long
OL,8,Fgone.
OL,10,FBut the friendships between the women,
OL,11,Fsparked through the hardships of the
OL,12,Fstrike, still burn bright. That year,
OL,13,Fthat epic struggle, will never be
OL,14,Fforgotten.
