OL,3,CThe women who were pivotal in allowing
OL,4,Cthe miners to strike
OL,6,FActivist Sian James told ITV Wales: "A
OL,7,Fcrystallising moment for me was when
OL,8,FMargaret Thatcher and Ian MacGregor
OL,9,Fdescribed us as 'the enemy within'.
OL,10,FAnd I remember sitting there in front
OL,11,Fof the TV and thinking 'Right you
OL,12,Fthink I'm your enemy, I'll be the best
OL,13,Fenemy you've ever had. You'll be so
OL,14,Fsorry you even said that."
OL,16,FShe added: "Then we had to step up. We
OL,17,Flooked at each other as a young couple
OL,18,Fwith kids and we said, that's it we've
OL,19,Fgot to do more.
